---
// src/components/StoryFriends.astro
---
<section class="py-24 lg:py-32 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 bg-appleGray-50 dark:bg-appleGray-950 border-t border-appleGray-200 dark:border-appleGray-800">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto flex flex-col lg:flex-row items-center gap-16">
    <div class="flex-1 space-y-6">
      <span class="text-indigo-500 font-semibold tracking-wider uppercase text-sm">Chapter 02</span>
      <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold">My Friends</h2>
      <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-appleGray-600 dark:text-appleGray-400 leading-relaxed font-light">
        Friends are the family we choose. Late-night conversations, spontaneous adventures, and endless laughter. 
        Here's to the people who make the journey so incredibly fun and worthwhile.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="flex-1 w-full flex gap-4 lg:gap-6">
      <div class="space-y-4 lg:space-y-6 flex-1">
        <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1529156069898-49953eb1b5ce?q=80&w=800&auto=format&fit=crop" alt="Friends laughing" class="zoomable w-full h-40 sm:h-56 object-cover rounded-2xl cursor-zoom-in hover:shadow-xl transition-all" />
        <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1543807535-eceef0bc6599?q=80&w=800&auto=format&fit=crop" alt="Group of friends" class="zoomable w-full h-56 sm:h-72 object-cover rounded-2xl cursor-zoom-in hover:shadow-xl transition-all" />
      </div>
      <div class="space-y-4 lg:space-y-6 flex-1 mt-12 lg:mt-16">
        <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1539635278303-d4002c07eae3?q=80&w=800&auto=format&fit=crop" alt="Friends traveling" class="zoomable w-full h-64 sm:h-80 object-cover rounded-2xl cursor-zoom-in hover:shadow-xl transition-all" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
